OL,3,CResidents call on South West Water
OL,4,Cboss to resign over town's parasite
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FA mother from Brixham has told ITV
OL,8,FNews West Country she believes the
OL,9,Fboss of South West Water (SWW) should
OL,10,Fresign over the company's handling of
OL,11,Fthe cryptosporidium outbreak.
OL,13,FMichaela Lewis' three-year-old son and
OL,14,Ffive-year-old daughter are showing
OL,15,Fsymptoms of the illness caused by the
OL,16,Fbacteria. She says she believes their
OL,17,Fsickness bugs are linked to the
OL,18,Fcontamination.
