OL,3,CResidents call on South West Water
OL,4,Cboss to resign over town's parasite
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FChief executive Susan Davy has
OL,8,Fpreviously apologised for the
OL,9,Fdisruption, saying she was "truly
OL,10,Fsorry" for the spread of the parasite.
OL,12,FSo far, there have been 57 confirmed
OL,13,Fcases of the illness caused by it with
OL,14,Fmore than 100 others reporting
OL,15,Fsymtpoms.
OL,17,FAround 2,500 properties in the
OL,18,FHillhead area of the seaside town are
OL,19,Fstill being advised to boil their
OL,20,Fwater following the outbreak seven
OL,21,Fdays ago.
