OL,3,CResidents call on South West Water
OL,4,Cboss to resign over town's parasite
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FMichaela told ITV News she believes
OL,8,Fchief executive Susan Davy should now
OL,9,Fstep down from her role.
OL,11,F"They told us the water was safe, and
OL,12,Fthey didn't have the evidence to back
OL,13,Fthat up," she said.
OL,15,F"They said 'testing at our treatment
OL,16,Ffacility said it was safe'. They
OL,17,Fdidn't test our taps."
OL,19,FMs Lewis has a background in
OL,20,Fenvironmental health and believes the
OL,21,Fspread could have been avoided.
