OL,3,CResidents call on South West Water
OL,4,Cboss to resign over town's parasite
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"I'm very good at reading and
OL,8,Funderstanding regulations, so I can
OL,9,Fsee where they have gone horribly
OL,10,Fwrong and what should have been done
OL,11,Fto better protect the people of
OL,12,FBrixham," she said.
OL,14,F"It was absolutely avoidable," she
OL,15,Fadded.
OL,17,FMichaela's neighbour Tanya Matthews
OL,18,Fsaid: "It says an awful lot that
OL,19,F(Susan Davy) won't speak to any
OL,20,Fresidents or any media."
