OL,7,FThe water company has also , despite
OL,8,Fthe criticism it has faced following
OL,9,Fthe outbreak.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, SWW has announced it will
OL,12,Foffer #215 in compensation for those
OL,13,Fwho have been impacted.
OL,15,FThe town's MP, Anthony Mangnall MP has
OL,16,Fsaid Pennon, SWW's parent company,
OL,17,Fshould suspend the dividend payments
OL,18,Fthis year, or the company's CEO should
OL,19,Fresign.
