OL,7,FBosses at the water company say they
OL,8,Fare working "24 hours a day" to solve
OL,9,Fthe issue.
OL,11,FDavid Harris, SWW's incident director,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our teams on the ground
OL,13,Fcontinue to work as quickly as we can
OL,14,Fto resolve the situation in the
OL,15,FHillhead supply area, where we are
OL,16,Fstill advising around 2,500 properties
OL,17,Fto boil their drinking water before
OL,18,Fconsuming.
