OL,7,F"We are urgently investigating the
OL,8,Fdamaged air valve on private land
OL,9,Fwhich we believe to be the probable
OL,10,Fcause, and following the draining and
OL,11,Fcleaning of Hillhead reservoir we have
OL,12,Fnow refilled the largest of the two
OL,13,Ftanks within the reservoir and we have
OL,14,Fisolated the second tank.
