OL,3,CResidents call on South West Water
OL,4,Cboss to resign over town's parasite
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"We are working 24 hours a day, and
OL,8,Fearly this morning we commenced
OL,9,Fflushing of the wider Hillhead network
OL,10,Fas we work to eliminate any traces of
OL,11,Fcryptosporidium. We will not lift the
OL,12,Fboil water notice in Hillhead until we
OL,13,Fand our public health partners are
OL,14,Fcompletely satisfied it is safe to do
OL,15,Fso.
OL,17,F"Our bottled water stations in
OL,18,FBroadsands, Freshwater Quarry and
OL,19,FChurston remain open to customers
OL,20,Facross the Brixham area between 7am
OL,21,Fand 9pm daily."
