OL,7,F"We encourage residents to follow good
OL,8,Fhygiene practices to prevent onward
OL,9,Fspread of infection. Along with
OL,10,Feffective public health measures,
OL,11,Fincluding the boil water notice for
OL,12,Fareas where it still applies, we are
OL,13,Fconfident that the right steps are
OL,14,Fbeing taken to ensure our residents
OL,15,Fand visitors are no longer at risk.
